snippet.title: FIFA 15 (PC) - Gameplay
snippet.description:
FIFA 15 is a football simulation video game developed by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts under the EA Sports label. On PC for the first time, FIFA 15 runs on EA's Ignite engine with the same features as the PlayStation 3 and Xbox 360 editions.

▌PC Gameplays Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLXEHhSievieFw3PRaPmrVQ4mTjr4BMRE0

💰 Here you can buy games at good prices: https://www.g2a.com/n/ncgyt
